Name: Seek Girl
About the game: This is a 'collection game' which unlocks 'collection' girls by tapping cute little people who jump out of the hole. The unlocked girl will be sealed in a bottle and you can meet her again at any time. Every beautiful girl has her own unique movements and voice to make you have a more authentic experience! Game features Leisure Play + Girl Animation + Passionate Voice Every girl has her own elf guardian in her heart. When you capture his elf, you can get her girl's heart.~
